@startuml
!theme plain
title Component Diagram – High Level Architecture

package "ASP.NET Core Web API" {
    [Controllers] as Ctrl
    [Repositories] as Repo
    [Strategies] as Strat
    [Services] as Svc
    [Entity Framework Core] as EF
}

database "Oracle Database 21c XE" as DB

[Thunder Client] as Client
[Swagger UI] as Swagger

Client --> Ctrl : HTTP requests
Swagger --> Ctrl : HTTP requests

Ctrl --> Repo : uses
Ctrl --> Strat : uses
Ctrl --> Svc : uses

Repo --> EF : calls
Strat --> EF : calls
Svc --> (no DB)

EF --> DB : SQL queries

note right of Ctrl
  Controllers:
  - ProductsController
  - IndexingDemoController
  - QueryOptimizationController
  - ConcurrencyDemoController
  - AsyncVsSyncController
end note

note right of Repo
  Repository Pattern
  IProductRepository / ProductRepository
end note

note right of Strat
  Strategy Pattern
  Indexed / NonIndexed / RawSql
end note

note right of Svc
  Singleton Pattern
  BenchmarkService
end note

@enduml